        <h2>About VideoTube</h2>
        <p>VideoTube is a comprehensive backend API designed for video streaming platforms, aiming to provide a robust
            foundation for a YouTube-like experience. With VideoTube, developers can integrate powerful features,
            enabling seamless video uploads, engaging user interactions, and personalized experiences.</p>
    </section>

