            <li><i class="fas fa-comments"></i> <strong>User Interaction:</strong> Comments, likes, and subscriptions to
                foster community engagement.</li>
            <li><i class="fas fa-list-alt"></i><strong>Playlists:</strong> Create and manage playlists for
                customized
                video collections.</li>
            <li><i class="fas fa-bell"></i> <strong>Subscriptions:</strong> Stay updated on favorite channels and
                content creators.</li>
            <li><i class="fas fa-share-alt"></i> <strong>Social Media:</strong> Unique tweeting feature for sharing and
                interacting beyond the platform.</li>
        </ul>
